Complex example
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

In this example we will disable the Index module and move REST module to ``http://api.example.com/`` and ``http://rest.example.com``.

.. code:: text

   http {
       index (active: false) {}
       rest {
           context-path = '/'
           vhosts = [ 'api.example.com', 'rest.example.com' ]
       }
   }